    "actor_description": "It lands in me like a click-quiet, mechanical certainty. My body believes it before my mind tries to argue it down: shoulders set, spine lengthening, breath deeper. I don't feel the need to announce anything. I just know, cleanly, that I did what I said I would do. The satisfaction isn't loud-it's steady, like weight finally balanced where it belongs.",
